attributes.review: I downloaded this app to support our lord and savior, but soon after started having strange things happen around my house. On my way in from a brisk evening walk in the old country, I noticed my front door was ajar, but no one was home. I entered the house to see that all of the cupboards in my kitchen had been opened and filled to the brim with MAGA hats - this normally wouldn’t be a problem but I sure didn’t buy all of those, maybe only 5 were mine. Then I went upstairs and my bathtub was full of water, and the strange thing was the tiny confederate flags that seemed to have been shoved so deep inside my plumbing that my toilet was overflowing with deep seeded racism, misinformation, and, you guessed it, senseless murder by my boys in blue. I tried flushing but I couldn’t seem to unclog the states rights propaganda from my little toilet pipes. I brushed it off and got in bed only to find that there was cheetoh dust covering my brand new white robes - I HAD JUST GOTTEN THOSE. Anyways, I had to uninstall this app due to the haunting reminder of our nations racist past.
